ids/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/diary18.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5,1,'2014-01-16 05:43:15','2014-01-16 05:43:15','<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The Handmaids Orphanages are a place for slum and underprivileged children to grow up and get an education.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">There are currently two main locations in greater Mumbai, India: Sahar (Church Pakdi) Slum and Merces-Giriz</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">They have been in existence for more than 20 years</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">They are run by an order of nuns known as the Handmaids of the Blessed Trinity (HMBT)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">They developed as a result of the HMBT outreach work in the slums of Mumbai</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>','About','','trash','open','open','','about','','','2014-02-26 01:48:21','2014-02-26 01:48:21','',0,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/?page_id=5',1,'page','',0),(6,1,'2014-01-16 05:43:15','2014-01-16 05:43:15','','About','','inherit','open','open','','5-revision-v1','','','2014-01-16 05:43:15','2014-01-16 05:43:15','',5,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/uncategorized/5-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(7,1,'2014-01-16 05:43:47','2014-01-16 05:43:47','On this page you will see a brief biographical sketch of key people of the HMBT','Sister Bios','','publish','open','closed','','stories','','','2014-03-10 16:34:51','2014-03-10 16:34:51','',0,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/?page_id=7',4,'page','',0),(175,1,'2014-02-26 05:10:27','2014-02-26 05:10:27','This is a log of a visit to the HMBT orphanages written by a','Diary of a Visit','','inherit','open','open','','9-autosave-v1','','','2014-02-26 05:10:27','2014-02-26 05:10:27','',9,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/uncategorized/9-autosave-v1',0,'revision','',0),(8,1,'2014-01-16 05:43:34','2014-01-16 05:43:34','','Stories','','inherit','open','open','','7-revision-v1','','','2014-01-16 05:43:34','2014-01-16 05:43:34','',7,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/uncategorized/7-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(9,1,'2014-01-16 05:44:36','2014-01-16 05:44:36','This is a log of a visit to the HMBT orphanages in December, 2009 written by a 13 year old girl and her father.','Diary of a Visit','','publish','open','closed','','diary-of-a-visit','','','2014-03-10 16:35:17','2014-03-10 16:35:17','',0,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/?page_id=9',5,'page','',0),(173,1,'2014-03-10 00:55:21','2014-03-10 00:55:21','The HMBT order has relied entirely on receiving outside donations and generating of funds from within.  There is no steady stream of funding coming from any parent organization.   The HMBT is registered as an Indian NGO under the secular name Sneha Jewan Kendra which means Love and Life Center.  Effort is currently underway to register Sneha Jewan Kendra in the United States as a charitable 501 C 3 organization\n\nOn this page you can see a list of the major current needs at the orphanages.  Your contribution is greatly appreciated.','Give','','inherit','open','open','','11-autosave-v1','','','2014-03-10 00:55:21','2014-03-10 00:55:21','',11,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/uncategorized/11-autosave-v1',0,'revision','',0),(10,1,'2014-01-16 05:44:36','2014-01-16 05:44:36','','Visitor Logs','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision-v1','','','2014-01-16 05:44:36','2014-01-16 05:44:36','',9,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/uncategorized/9-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(11,1,'2014-01-16 05:44:48','2014-01-16 05:44:48','The HMBT order has relied entirely on receiving outside donations and generating of funds from within.  There is no steady stream of funding coming from any parent organization.   The HMBT is registered as an Indian NGO under the secular name Sneha Jewan Kendra which means Love and Life Center.  Effort is currently underway to register Sneha Jewan Kendra in the United States as a charitable 501 C 3 organization.\r\n\r\nOn this page you can see a list of the major current needs at the orphanages.  Your contribution is greatly appreciated.','Give','','publish','open','closed','','give','','','2014-03-10 16:35:32','2014-03-10 16:35:32','',0,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/?page_id=11',6,'page','',0),(12,1,'2014-01-16 05:44:48','2014-01-16 05:44:48','','Give','','inherit','open','open','','11-revision-v1','','','2014-01-16 05:44:48','2014-01-16 05:44:48','',11,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/uncategorized/11-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(13,1,'2014-01-17 04:33:39','2014-01-17 04:33:39','<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A safe and nurturing orphanage environment</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For slum and underprivileged children to grow up and get an education.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Two main locations in Mumbai, India</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Run by an order of nuns known as the Handmaids of the Blessed Trinity (HMBT) since 1989</li>\r\n</ul>','Home','','publish','open','closed','','home','','','2014-03-11 00:33:59','2014-03-11 00:33:59','',0,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/?page_id=13',0,'page','',0),(211,1,'2014-03-10 00:25:49','2014-03-10 00:25:49','<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">A safe and nurturing orphanage environment</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For slum and underprivileged children to grow up and get an education.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Two main locations in Mumbai, India</p>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">Run by an order of nuns known as the Handmaids of the Blessed Trinity (HMBT) since 1989</li>\r\n</ul>','Home','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-v1','','','2014-03-10 00:25:49','2014-03-10 00:25:49','',13,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/uncategorized/13-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(179,1,'2014-02-2